videos.headline: Tulane on the scoreboard first against Memphis
videos.description: Tulane's Corey Dauphine rushes up the middle for a touchdown to give the Green Wave a 7-0 lead over Memphis.

videos.headline: Memphis' Henderson breaks loose for a 47-yard score
videos.description: Tigers' running back Darrell Henderson runs 47 yards to the house and ties the game up at 7-7.

videos.headline: Green Wave RB goes 53-yards untouched for a score
videos.description: Darius Bradwell gives Tulane their second big touchdown run of the first quarter on a 53-yard run.

videos.headline: Henderson doing it all
videos.description: Memphis' Darrell Henderson catches and runs for a 43-yard score to cut Memphis' deficit to 17-14.

videos.headline: Tulane ends third quarter with 51-yard TD
videos.description: Justin McMillan connects with Darnell Mooney for a Tulane 51-yard touchdown to end the third quarter.

videos.headline: Tulane defense forces safety
videos.description: Juan Monjarres forces fumble that is recovered by Memphis in their own end zone resulting in a safety.

videos.headline: Dauphine rushes for his second TD of the game
videos.description: Running back Corey Dauphine out runs Memphis defense for a 46-yard score.
